{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762168257167","path":null,"data":{"id":3938,"title":"AIA:個人意外保障產品保費調整","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1744024705497,"tags":["友邦保險"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">致合作夥伴:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; AIA一直致力為客戶提供優質個人意外保障產品，今次就<span style=\"color: #e92360;\"><strong>2025年個人意外保障產品</strong></span>作出保費調整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>一.保費調整</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>指定個人意外保障產品</strong>的保費將於<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d; text-decoration: underline;\">2025年4月17日或以後</span></strong></span>之保單週年日起作出調整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2025-04-07/blobid0_b317a2883c1248c395355db8b7f596d8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>二.保單預繳保費安排</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong>客戶繳付之金額<span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">(包括所有就該保單之預繳保費)</span></strong>於扣除該保單年度之保費後，<strong><span style=\"color: #e92360;\">餘數將存於現金儲備金戶口內積存生息<span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">(息率為非保證)</span></span></strong>，並且客戶可隨時提取或用作繳付保費。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e92360; text-decoration: underline;\">請注意，如於現金儲備金戶口內的總金額不足繳付未來保費，客戶需恢復繳付所需的保費</span></strong></span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"Ref_A2025074.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2025-04-07/Ref_A2025074_fe9df6d99fb649c7b0e133a5e173f4e3.pdf","uploadTime":1743996185094,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"AIA","companyName":"友邦保險","productCodes":["AIA:PSAMER","AIA:AIR","AIA:LSPAI"],"productNames":["自選人身意外保險 - 意外醫療賠償","全意保綜合意外保險附加契約","個人意外保險"],"companyCodes":["AIA"],"companyNames":["友邦保險"],"startEffectiveDate":1744024887677,"endEffectiveDate":null,"effective":true}}